#======================================================================
# BUILD TEX
#======================================================================

1. Set perspective file as thesis.tex
2. Set builder as Quick Build
3. Press blue arrow

#======================================================================
# BUILD NOMENCLATURE
#======================================================================

1. Set perspective file as thesis.tex
2. Set builder as PDFLateX
3. Press blue arrow
4. Open CMD (Window OS) / Terminal (Linux OS) as project root
5. Run command: makeindex thesis.nlo -s nomencl.ist -o thesis.nls
6. Re-run step 2, 3 => #BUILD TEX

#======================================================================
# BUILD BIBLIOGRAPHY
#======================================================================

1. Set perspective file as thesis.tex
2. Set builder as PDFLateX
3. Press blue arrow
4. Set builder as BibTeX
5. Press blue arrow
6. Re-run step 2, 3 => #BUILD TEX
